{"tid":1212024,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"明明睇片就好多人受傷，但真係有follow up都係一兩個人","createTime":"2019-06-12T17:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T21:20:41.000Z","uid":174979,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c72db9145f91fb5c111c051bd319199ef6605c12","tid":1212024,"uid":174979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:08:39.000Z","msg":"首先呢位義士，我係第一張見到有流血嘅相，當時仲話急救都無反應<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SAUdxQo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSAUdxQo.png&h=defbf046&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n唔知佢去咗邊間醫院，亦唔似RTHK員工咁去埋醫院睇傷勢。<br />\n<br />\n跟住到睇片畀六個防暴圍毆嘅黑衫義士，又係唔知有無送到上白車同傷勢如何。<br />\n<br />\n仲有一個着綠色衫嘅義士畀黑警拖撚住行都無哂反應，行入轉角就唔見咗。<br />\n<br />\n仲有仲有，好似係腹部中彈嘅叔叔訓咗喺地，被黑警拖走之後又唔知有無送去醫院。<br />\n<br />\n仲有畀一班黑警圍毆嘅女仔又無報導佢傷勢<br />\n<br />\n真係好擔心所有受咗傷嘅義士"},{"pid":"3d7e09f9bfb73a051601b8a5485fd2fff297f12f","tid":1212024,"uid":174979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:13:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537b0355f92f75d2aee3d0a1182776c970e35335","tid":1212024,"uid":174979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:14:41.000Z","msg":"有無醫護人員知道"},{"pid":"ab860196fa15fa15d7263dd89bdd22b544d2f739","tid":1212024,"uid":54719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:14:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac78f07cb848dc2902567de7c3f7f458479bf326","tid":1212024,"uid":172024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:15:54.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"8f41ae5e45c74214bf043e6a107034ebd26666d2","tid":1212024,"uid":174979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:16:03.000Z","msg":"點解無哂聲氣，仲有嘔血嗰個義士<br />\n同17歲少女宜家到底係點"},{"pid":"6460d7b60c6f798b316e3eb623248348164e9683","tid":1212024,"uid":174979,"like":2